content:
How can I replace the term that matches the assigned numeric value with an opposing word to the initial term provided in the following JSON data? The task is extremely enjoyable and the quantity is two.
{
  "textual_expression": "The endeavor of performing this task is extremely enjoyable",
  "numerical_value": 2,
  "word_replacements": {
    "endeavor": "quagmire",
    "performing": "ceasing"
  }
}
